dc_title_s: Plan of Atlantic City Terrace and Atlantic City Gardens, Longport, N.J.
dc_description_s: Map featuring beachfront property lots of Atlantic City Terrace and Atlantic City Gardens in Longport, N.J.|Handwritten scale on map denotes 1" = 160', and that it is an office copy implying that this map is 1/2 the size of the original|Date of 1906 is handwritten on map and is not necessarily the date map was produced.
